<!-- src/EduPlatform.Web/Areas/Instructor/Views/Course/Create.cshtml -->
@model EduPlatform.Web.ViewModels.Instructor.AddCourseViewModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "إضافة كورس جديد";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container-fluid py-4">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="card shadow border-0">
                <div class="card-header bg-gradient-primary text-white py-3">
                    <h4 class="mb-0">
                        <i class="fas fa-plus-circle me-2"></i>
                        إضافة كورس جديد
                    </h4>
                </div>

                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    @if (TempData["Error"] != null)
                    {
                        <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
                            @TempData["Error"]
                            <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                        </div>
                    }

                    <form asp-action="Create" method="post">
                        @Html.AntiForgeryToken()

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label asp-for="Title" class="form-label fw-bold">
                                <i class="fas fa-heading text-primary me-1"></i>
                                عنوان الكورس
                            </label>
                            <input asp-for="Title" class="form-control form-control-lg"
                                   placeholder="مثال: اللغة العربية للصف الأول الثانوي" required />
                            <span asp-validation-for="Title" class="text-danger small"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label asp-for="SubjectId" class="form-label fw-bold">
                                <i class="fas fa-book text-primary me-1"></i>
                                المادة الدراسية
                            </label>
                            <select asp-for="SubjectId" class="form-select form-select-lg" required>
                                <option value="">-- اختر المادة --</option>
                                @if (ViewBag.Subjects != null)
                                {
                                    @foreach (var subject in ViewBag.Subjects)
                                    {
                                        <option value="@subject.Value">@subject.Text</option>
                                    }
                                }
                            </select>
                            <span asp-validation-for="SubjectId" class="text-danger small"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label asp-for="Description" class="form-label fw-bold">
                                <i class="fas fa-align-left text-primary me-1"></i>
                                وصف الكورس
                            </label>
                            <textarea asp-for="Description" class="form-control" rows="4"
                                      placeholder="وصف مختصر لمحتوى الكورس..."></textarea>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Description" class="text-danger small"></span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <label asp-for="Price" class="form-label fw-bold">
                                <i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave text-success me-1"></i>
                                سعر الاشتراك (جنيه)
                            </label>
                            <div class="input-group input-group-lg">
                                <input asp-for="Price" class="form-control" type="number"
                                       min="0" step="0.01" required />
                                <span class="input-group-text bg-light">ج.م</span>
                            </div>
                            <span asp-validation-for="Price" class="text-danger small"></span>
                        </div>

                        <hr class="my-4" />

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">


                            


                            <a href="/Instructor/Course/Index" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right me-2"></i>
                                رجوع
                            </a>


                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-5">
                                <i class="fas fa-save me-2"></i>
                                حفظ الكورس
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@section Scripts {
    @{
        await Html.RenderPartialAsync("_ValidationScriptsPartial");
    }
}